      "message": "It might be better to avoid duplication:\n\n```\nbaseMW :\u003d ...\nbaseAuthMW :\u003d baseMW.Extend(\n  middleware.WithContextTimeout(time.Minute),\n  auth.Authenticate(server.CookieAuth, \u0026server.OAuth2Method{Scopes: []string{server.EmailScope}}),\n)\nhtmlMW :\u003d baseAuthMW.Extend(\n  withAccessClientMiddleware,\n  ...\n)\n\n...\n\nr.GET(\"/auth-state\", baseAuthMW, ...)\n\n```\n\n(this has a caveat that \"/auth-state\" will actually not work when it is authenticated via access tokens and  \u0026server.OAuth2Method{...}).",
